{"tid":1170339,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【你懂的】國內票房無法超越《戰狼2》、《流浪地球》！中國禁《復仇者聯盟4》延長映期","createTime":"2019-05-25T02:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T06:56:59.000Z","uid":209140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4444c8e6ebf5cb4f27f77de62cd6b0a479db46f","tid":1170339,"uid":209140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:45:42.000Z","msg":"全球熱賣的Marvel電影《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》在中國大陸落畫，總票房為42.4億元人民幣，是中國電影史上最賣座的外語片。若計及所有電影，《復4》票房則位列第3，僅次於《戰狼2》（56.81億人民幣）及《流浪地球》（46.55億人民幣）。《復4》於4月24日在中國上映，即使票房大賣，仍不獲當局批准延長映期，只能上映1個月。最近中美貿易戰再起，兩國關係緊張，中國當局此舉被部份網民解讀為不希望《復4》打破《戰狼2》的票房紀錄。但亦有中國網民反駁稱，《戰狼2》1個月的票房已超過53億人民幣，即時只計算1個月的標準映期，《復4》仍然被比下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZANmRs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZANmRs.png&h=794117a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美貿易談判陷入停滯，美國政府將華為列入黑名單，而海康威視等5家中國企業亦被傳將會遭美國封殺。中央電視台電影頻道（CCTV-6）早前更調動節目，一連三晚播出講述韓戰歷史的抗美援朝戰爭片《英雄兒女》、《上甘嶺》及《奇襲》，政治含意明顯。近日有傳中國政府將參考以前的限韓令推出「限美令」，禁止美國影視作品或任何「親美」相關題材在大陸播出，此舉或將重創荷李活電影的票房。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0MobOv7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0MobOv7.png&h=482a6931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日中國網上更流傳以下短訊：「各位影視項目負責同志請特別注意，我們所有項目請勿使用美國藝人、美國主創，更不要選擇赴美拍攝。如有類似計劃請更改，特殊情況請報告！」<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：綜合報導"},{"pid":"0cb95ba75c9fdd4428cbedb99d8089a7a591e165","tid":1170339,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:48:55.000Z","msg":"戰狼個d係俾人迫去睇<br />\n點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449b380f6f62048b73614c65c9a5f0456894628f","tid":1170339,"uid":155095,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1526094626614a5a8f3c0c7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F1526094626614a5a8f3c0c7&h=1746fba5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f870338a590b15d7499de3c14344363cbd6fe8a0","tid":1170339,"uid":209140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"449b380f6f62048b73614c65c9a5f0456894628f","tid":1170339,"uid":155095,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1526094626614a5a8f3c0c7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp3.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F1526094626614a5a8f3c0c7&h=1746fba5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac766cca51fd13deaf34aa2473c3844ce342bc4","tid":1170339,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"真係唔好彩 本來有機會登頂影史票房第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3466f4fbe2047490861a6cdd251e356bc99a1b","tid":1170339,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:56:59.000Z","msg":"戰狼篤大，穫仇者篤細，差唔多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}